WEBVTT

1
00:18:51.890 --> 00:18:53.530 
被送到那里去的人
the people that are sent to this place

2
00:18:53.530 --> 00:18:56.430 
绝对不能再出来
should not be allowed out into the real world.

3
00:18:56.430 --> 00:18:58.150 
他们任何一人都能搅得天翻地覆
Every one of them is a potential game changer.

4
00:18:58.540 --> 00:18:59.630 
或许更糟
For the worse.

5
00:18:59.630 --> 00:19:00.730 
明白
All right.

6
00:19:05.200 --> 00:19:07.970 
行动指南?
Guidelines?

7
00:19:07.970 --> 00:19:10.000 
和平常一样 用化名 编造身世
The usual. Full work. Alias. Cover story.

8
00:19:10.020 --> 00:19:11.440 
联系人 行动代号
Contact. Evac number. Right?

9
00:19:11.450 --> 00:19:13.200 
唯一的区别是
Well, the only difference is

10
00:19:13.200 --> 00:19:14.880 
为了全面测试那里的安全性
to fully test the security of the system

11
00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:16.510 
不能告诉你们任何人
it's essential that none of you

12
00:19:16.520 --> 00:19:17.720 
监狱的位置
know the location of the incarceration.

13
00:19:19.050 --> 00:19:20.650 
有问题吗?
Will that present a problem?

14
00:19:20.650 --> 00:19:22.040 
当然有问题
Yes. Yes, it would.

